segue_dave.line: The Lemonheads started being a band in 1984, while Foghat's "Take It Or Leave It" was released by Bearsville Records, a record label which dissolved in the same year...
segue_dave.explanation: The Lemonheads started being a band in 1984 and Foghat's "Fool For The City" was released by Bearsville Records, a record label that stop existing in the same year.
